      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry (identical to the simulation geometry) operated at the same five flow-speed combinations as the COU operating points. Blood analog fluid (bovine blood, hematocrit-matched) and temperature conditions match COU operating envelope. The validation activities span the full COU operating envelope without extrapolation. Gap clearance was set to nominal value; sensitivity to clearance variation is addressed in the sensitivity analysis. Validation activities are assessed as directly relevant to the COU with no significant domain gaps.",
