        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Model form acceptance criterion",
        "description": "Turbulence model selection must be justified with reference to published validation evidence for rotating machinery. Hemolysis model must be an FDA-recognized correlation. Non-Newtonian blood rheology must be included. Alternative model form sensitivity must be assessed."
