      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "All model inputs are documented with sources and uncertainty estimates. Geometry: FDA generic pump CAD (dimensional tolerance ±50 µm verified by CMM). Boundary conditions: inlet flow rate from Coriolis meter (±0.5%), rotational speed from encoder (±10 RPM). Blood properties: viscosity from literature (Cho and Kensey 1991, ±8%), density 1060±10 kg/m³. Hemolysis model constants (α, β, C) from Giersiepen et al. (1990) with published uncertainty ranges. Input uncertainty propagated through Monte Carlo analysis (2000 samples) to quantify contribution to output uncertainty.",
