      "rationale": "Hemolysis experiments performed using fresh bovine blood from a single donor per test session, with hematocrit adjusted to 35±2% using centrifugation and resuspension. Three independent test repetitions performed at each of the 5 operating points (15 total test runs). Blood age < 4 hours at start of test. Baseline plasma free hemoglobin (pfHb) measured before each run; runs with pfHb > 20 mg/dL excluded (none excluded). Sample preparation and handling documented in experimental protocol EP-2024-007.",
